🧠 Mental Map for Distinct Subsequences

Distinct Subsequences
           │
           ├─ Break strings into prefixes
           │
           ├─ Make DP table (grid)
           │
           ├─ Base case: empty t → 1 way
           │
           ├─ Fill table:
           │      ├─ Match → use + skip (add diagonal + top-left)
           │      └─ No match → skip (take top)
           │
           ├─ Solve small → big prefixes
           │
           └─ Result: bottom-right cell = number of distinct subsequences

📦 Complexity

Time : O(N × M)

Space : O(N × M) → can optimize to O(M)

